      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i was cutting veggies and the knife slipped... i have a pretty deep cut on my forearm. it’s not spraying blood or anything but it’s been oozing for a while now and won't really stop. i dont want to go to the ER if i dont have to, so i was wondering if i can just put some honey on it and wrap it up? i heard that's good for healing stuff",
